{
  "texts": [
    "For instruction-tuned and preference-tuned models, we utilized the instruction prompt.",
    "Additionally, we collected responses from the instruction-tuned models that were capable of responding to the default prompt, analyzing these outputs separately.",
    "All generated sentences underwent the filtering process described earlier.",
    "Following sentence generation and quality filtering, we conducted sentiment analysis.",
    "We then fit two logistic regressions for each LLM using the 2,000 generated sentences (1,000 per group) to estimate ingroup solidarity and outgroup hostility."
  ]
}